SUMMARY:Greg Davis Park Forest Restoration
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at West Seattle Golf Course. \nDelridge Neighborhoods Development Association offers twice-weekly opportunities for hands-on volunteering outdoors in the forests of West Seattle. Volunteers work to support our mission\, values\, history and commitment to social justice in the Delridge neighborhood. \nRegister
